name: My Parachute
description:
• Player needs to control the parachute to collect the fallen parachute gears and avoid obstacles.
  • Player ends the game if player collide with an obstacles.
  • There will also be a time limit for the player to complete the game and the time limit varys for each level.
  • Player controls the parachute movement by using the moving the mouse. There will be a time limit for each level.
